apps.description:
Lisa is a famous designer. She had planned to return to her home town to reopen grandma's hotel. But when she returned, the hotel has become dilapidated. To make matters worse, she lost all her luggage and even found a baby in here! She's hungry and cold, please play the game to collect resources to help Lisa and repair her hotel. Complete her various interesting room designs to help people here live a better life! 

Gameplay:
Design personalized rooms for all kinds of people;
Solve challenging bubble puzzles; 
Uncover the story of the protagonist;
When you complete the cloakroom, you can unlock the costume play to dress Lisa and her dog guests;
And when Lucky Hotel is completed, you can unlock the town map, find "foster hill" and "mountain campground";
Unlock dog racing, hot air balloon race, simulation store and other gameplay...

We will regularly update the game content and provide rich furniture decoration.
Let's join the protagonist for an exciting story!

Contact us:
supports@dragonpopstudio.com

